{"tid":1323776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外電指華為有意裁減美國子公司1千職位","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T03:15:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4c0f01c950749c53af6fc71e6dbabfebdb844d","tid":1323776,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"外電指華為有意裁減美國子公司1千職位<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468674-20190716.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468674-20190716.htm&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeQEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=71ed5987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468674-20190716.htm&h=7c52675f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468674-20190716.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外電報道，中國電訊設備商華為有意在美國子公司裁減1千名員工。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，受影響的華為子公司於華盛頓州、得州及加州都有分公司職位將被裁減。《路透社》引述華為一間位於意大利的子公司高層消息，表示若果華為下月仍然在美國制裁黑名單上，將會在美國裁員，同時在3年內，向意大利注資31億美元，以帶來1千個就業機會，確保零件供應穩定。<br />\n<br />\n美方一直游說意大利等其他歐洲國家不要使用華為設備。加拿大早前表示，考慮在10月大選後，才決定是否容許華為參與當地5G網絡建設。"},{"pid":"fde08e3a1c50dd890048b99f358157aa40bf6b20","tid":1323776,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}